name: Resemblance, World #23
description: Resemblance, The boy passed the test, he stood tall, as shocked as he was, he wrote up in his journal: "Who would belive the things I've seen, who would dare come close to me?" There she was, sitting all alone all this time, waiting for a wanderer. He saw her and it was the beginning. "Is she another monster?" he taught to himself... |Contact me on socials for more in-depth content!
